@startuml
hide footbox
actor "Admin" as Admin
boundary "DepartmentListPage.jsx" as ListUI
control "api.js" as FrontendAPI
control "departments_api" as API
entity "PhongBan" as DB

Admin -> ListUI: Click icon "Sửa"
activate ListUI
ListUI --> Admin: Hiển thị Modal (kèm dữ liệu cũ)

Admin -> ListUI: Sửa thông tin & Click "Lưu"
ListUI -> FrontendAPI: PUT /api/departments/{id}/
activate FrontendAPI
FrontendAPI -> API: Request cập nhật
activate API

API -> DB: Get & Update Department
activate DB
DB --> API: Success
deactivate DB

alt Thành công
    API --> FrontendAPI: {success: true}
    deactivate API
    FrontendAPI --> ListUI: Success
    deactivate FrontendAPI
    
    ListUI --> ListUI: Đóng Modal & Reload
    ListUI --> Admin: Thông báo thành công
else Lỗi
    activate API
    API --> FrontendAPI: {error: "..."}
    deactivate API
    activate FrontendAPI
    FrontendAPI --> ListUI: Error
    deactivate FrontendAPI
    ListUI --> Admin: Hiển thị lỗi
end

deactivate ListUI

@enduml
